data.description: Located in the community of Gramercy Farms in Saint Cloud, Florida. This Single Family Home features 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 car garage and big backyard, all fenced with gates in every side of the house, water sprinkle system, Hybrid water heater. Ceiling fans. Low HOA.  Gramercy Farms community boasts many amenities including playgrounds, parks, and ponds. In minutes you can hop onto Florida’s Turnpike which will whisk you to all parts of Central Florida including the theme parks, local shops and restaurants. Community is ideally located less than 20 minutes to Lake Nonas medical city, the 417 and 528, UCF Medical School, The VA Hospital and Nemours Childrens Hospital.  Gramercy Farms gives you access to Lake Nona area within 20-25 minutes, FL turnpike in 10-15 minutes, and MCO airport within 30-45 minutes. St. Cloud area offers restaurants, shopping and much more.  SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY!!!!
